If the primary class of \code{object} is \code{\link[stats:glm]{"glm"}}, then
\code{focus()} refits the model using \code{\link[brglm2:brglmFit]{brglm2::brglmFit()}} with \code{type = "ML"}
and starting values \code{coef(object)}.

